  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in the clay pot over medium heat.",
    "Sauté the chopped onion, ginger, and garlic until the onion is translucent.",
    "Add the crushed red chili and sauté for 1 minute.",
    "Add the coriander powder, turmeric powder, and garam masala powder. Cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the buckwheat flour and cook for 2 minutes, stirring constantly.",
    "Gradually add 2 cups of water, stirring continuously to prevent lumps.",
    "Bring the mixture to a boil, then reduce the heat to low and cover the pot.",
    "Simmer for 20 minutes or until the water is absorbed and the mixture has thickened.",
    "Garnish with chopped cilantro and serve hot.",
    "Let the biryani rest for 10 minutes before serving to allow the flavors to meld together."
  ],
